    <item>
      <title>警惕市场风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-07/consider-yourself-warned-on-market-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[很高兴看到今天早上股市站稳脚跟。但随着事态的逐渐好转，事实上，我们正在目睹一记警钟。这是对美国股市的警告，因为美国股市的定价仍然基本完美，并且有望软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-07/consider-yourself-warned-on-market-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者不愿购买收益率较低的 10 年期国债，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bonds-fall-as-traders-pounce-on-fragile-return-of-risk-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着本周早些时候席卷全球市场的动荡逐渐消退，美国国债价格正在下滑，投资者拒绝出售收益率较低的 10 年期国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bonds-fall-as-traders-pounce-on-fragile-return-of-risk-appetite</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行鸽派信号削弱进一步加息预期 日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会进一步提高基准利率，随后日元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
